  "projectName": "Accompanist Lyrics Core",
  "projectDescription": "A Kotlin Multiplatform library for parsing, converting, and exporting lyrics in formats like LRC, Enhanced LRC, TTML (Apple Music), Lyricify Syllable, and Kugou KRC.",
